{
  "texts": [
    "This transparency is vital for applications requiring trust and reliability, such as in medical diagnostics or autonomous vehicle navigation.",
    "Future research should focus on refining these interpretative capabilities to ensure AI decisions are understandable and justifiable by human standards.",
    "C. Considerations for Bias and FairnessAs with any AI system, the risk of bias in multimodal AI models is a concern.",
    "The integration of multiple data types can inadvertently amplify biases present in individual modalities.",
    "Future research must prioritize the development of methodologies to detect and mitigate these biases, ensuring that AI systems promote fairness and inclusivity."
  ]
}